title: Camp WeWow - Spider Week Day 5: Spider-cise!
description:
It's Day 5 of Spider Week, and we're hearing from campers who called in! To print your Web Weaver badge, head to tinkercast.com/camp. Thanks for joining us at Camp WeWow this summer! You can come back to this feed to join Mindy and Guy Raz on more scientific adventures every Monday and Friday. Happy trails, Campers!

See Privacy Policy at https://art19.com/privacy and California Privacy Notice at https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info.
